CapsLock RS is an independent Rust implementation of a Windows CapsLock
keyboard layer. The project is distributed under the Apache License, Version
2.0.

The product idea, keyboard-layer habits, INI naming style, and some action
names are inspired by CapsLock+:

  https://github.com/wo52616111/capslock-plus

CapsLock+ is licensed under GPLv2. CapsLock RS is not an official version or
successor of CapsLock+, and this repository is intended to avoid including
CapsLock+ source code. If GPLv2-covered source code is introduced later, the
project license and redistribution terms must be reviewed again before release.

Third-party dependency notices are listed in THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.